20 collateral received; and
21 2. Monthly reports showing total current liabilities, all bonds
22 written during the month by the professional bondsman or multicounty
23 agent bondsman and by any licensed bondsman who may countersign for
24 the professional bondsman or multicounty agent bondsman, all bonds
